Description.value:
Gets interchange/message payload from sender communication flow via ProcessDirect, identifies type system, calls the appropriate extraction flows or steps and writes the payload together with the extracted header parameters into message queue for the further processing in step 2.
In case of in case of XML based type systems, it calls separate extraction flows.
